[Quotes]
Victory0 = "Fear is necessary for evolution. The fear that one could be destroyed at any moment."
victory1 = "The Sosuke Aizen you knew...never existed to begin with."
victory2 = "Any betrayal you can see is trivial, what is truly frightening and much more lethal, is the betrayal you cannot see."
victory3 = "All creatures want to believe in something bigger than themselves. They cannot live without blind obedience"
victory4 = "I had no intention of deceiving anyone. It's just that none of you could understand...My true self."
victory5 = "Admiration is the furthest thing from understanding."
victory6 = "A victor must speak not of the current state of the world, but of how it should rightfully be."
